[[File:Astika lager beer.JPG|right|thumb|100px]] '''Astika''' is a [[Bulgaria]]n [[beer]] brand made in the city of [[Haskovo]] ({{lang-bg|Астика}}). The [[Astika Brewery]] was established in 1980, and in 1995 was bought by [[Kamenitza (company)|Kamenitza]], itself currently owned by [[Molson Coors]]. It has two brands – Astika Light (originally Astika Lux) and Astika Dark (5.6%, sold in winter). As of 2012, Astika is sold in 600 ml bottles, with a [[Pull-off bottle cap|pull-off top]], as well as 500ml cans as of 2017 that are priced at 1.05 лв Bulgarian lev
