{{further|Tatars|Tartary}} {{Hazara people}} '''Tatar Hazara''' ({{lang-fa|تاتار}}) is a [[Hazara tribes|tribe]] of [[Hazara people]]. They mainly live in [[Maymana]] Kotal area of [[Faryab Province]] in [[Afghanistan]] mostly with the neighboring of [[Uzbek people]], the same as other hazaras they have maintained all their [[Hazaragi culture|Hazaragi]] cultural habits. Tatar Hazaras speak [[Hazaragi dialect]] of [[Persian language|Persian]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.samangan.org/site2/index.php?route=news/view/&Nid=2690|title=دريچه ای برای همزيستی|website=www.samangan.org|access-date=2017-04-05}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=http://afghandata.org:8080/xmlui/handle/azu/225|title=پژوهشی در تاریخ هزاره‌ها، نویسنده:حسینعلی یزدانی بهسودی (حاج کاظم)|last=|first=|date=|publisher=چاپ خانه مهتاب|year=بهار 1368 خورشیدی|isbn=|location=Iran|pages=191&192}}</ref>
