{{Infobox company | name = Éditions du Rocher | logo = | type = [[Privately held company|Private]] | genre = | fate = | predecessor = | successor = | foundation = 1943 | founder = Charles Orengo | defunct = | location_city = | location_country = [[Monaco]] | location = 28 rue du Comte-Félix-Gastaldi | locations = | area_served = | key_people = | industry = | products = | production = | services = | revenue = | operating_income = | net_income = | aum = | assets = | equity = | owner = | num_employees = | parent = | divisions = | subsid = | homepage = | footnotes = | intl = }} The '''Éditions du Rocher''' is a publishing house based in [[Monaco]]. It publishes works of literature as well as books about current affairs and well-being. It was founded by Charles Orengo in 1943.<ref name="bnfeditionsdurocher">{{cite web|title=Éditions du Rocher|url=http://data.bnf.fr/14036336/editions_du_rocher/|website=Bibliothèque nationale de France|accessdate=April 20, 2017}}</ref> It was sold to [[Éditions Privat]] in 2005, [[Éditions Desclée de Brouwer]] in 2009, and [[Éditions Artège]] in 2014.<ref name="bnfeditionsdurocher"/><ref name="lemondebeuvemery">{{cite news|last1=Beuve-Méry|first1=Alain|title=Le groupe Artège rachète Desclée de Brouwer et les Editions du rocher|url=http://www.lemonde.fr/economie/article/2014/03/20/le-groupe-artege-rachete-desclee-de-brouwer-et-les-editions-du-rocher_4386810_3234.html|accessdate=April 21, 2017|work=Le Monde|date=March 20, 2014}}</ref>
